descriptionHtml: The U-Scale application is designed for all UMAX Smart Scales. You can clearly see many of your body values - weight, BMI, fat percentage, amount of water in the body and more. You can follow the trend of all values on a chart. The application supports multiple users, users in the same household, but you can also connect with friends or training coach remotely via the Internet.
